solution:
Here is the initial diagram:

[asy]
unitsize(1 cm);

pair A, B, C;

A = (0,2);
B = (-3,2);
C = (-3,0);

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw((-3.5,0)--(3.5,0));
draw((0,-3.5)--(0,3.5));

